				<td colspan="2"><span>No.  DX9 was an inevitable change because DX8 was simply outdated technology.  When they get the bugs out of DX9 (projection: February) it will actually run smoother than it did under  DX8 on most systems.  
<br />

<br />
Very few cards were unable to run DX9.  Those that were, were almost as old as EQ itself was.  Technology had to be updated for the game to continue improving, because face it, if EQ wants to last a few more years, it's going to badly need a facelift.</span></td>
